title: War of the Roses: Is It Okay to Cheat on a Cheater?
description: Olivia has cheated on her husband, Miles, in the past but they've worked through it and are still together.  But, Olivia is nervous Miles might be cheating on her now because he'll bring up that he has a "freebie".  Is he cheating and is it okay to cheat on a cheater?
